Package com.github.maxopoly.angeliacore.plugin.parameter

Annotation Type ParameterLoad

  • @Retention(RUNTIME)
@Target(FIELD)
public @interface ParameterLoad

    • Optional Element Summary

      Optional Elements 
      Modifier and Type Optional Element Description
      java.lang.String configId
      The path to use for this option when loading it from the plugins yaml config or an empty string if no path was specified
      java.lang.String id
      The identifier used for this option when parsing it from command line.
      boolean isRequired
      Is the parameter required? If set to true, an exception will be thrown if no option is given for it during plugin startup
      LoadPolicy policy
      Priorization order based on which is decided whether to use the direct input or yaml value

    • Element Detail

      • configId

        java.lang.String configId
        The path to use for this option when loading it from the plugins yaml config or an empty string if no path was specified
        Returns:
        Full YAML config path for this option
        Default:
        ""

      • id

        java.lang.String id
        The identifier used for this option when parsing it from command line. If this is not set, the variable name will be used
        Returns:
        Identifier used for this option or an empty string if the variable name should be used
        Default:
        ""

      • isRequired

        boolean isRequired
        Is the parameter required? If set to true, an exception will be thrown if no option is given for it during plugin startup
        Returns:
        Whether this option is required
        Default:
        false

      • policy

        LoadPolicy policy
        Priorization order based on which is decided whether to use the direct input or yaml value
        Returns:
        LoadPolicy used to decide which value to use
        Default:
        com.github.maxopoly.angeliacore.plugin.parameter.LoadPolicy.PRIORIZE_INPUT
